init_text: You're Barack Obama. 4 years into your retirement, you awake to find a letter with no return address on your bedside table. It reads "I hope you've had a chance to relax Barack...but pack your bags and call the number below. It's time to start the real job." Signed simply, "JFK."

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: You call the number and a man answers.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: He says his name is Jack Kennedy.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: He tells you that he's been watching you and he knows that you're the only man for the job.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: He tells you that you're the only man who can stop the Russians.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: You ask him what he means.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: He tells you that the Russians have been working on a project called "The Doomsday Device".

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: It's a device that will destroy the entire planet.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: He tells you that the Russians are planning to use it.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: He tells you that the Russians are afraid of the future.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: They're afraid of the way the world is changing.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: They're afraid of the way the world is becoming more open and free.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: They're afraid of the way that people are becoming more educated and more connected.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: They're afraid of the way that people are becoming more individualistic.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: They plan on living there while humanity dies.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: Jack tells you that you're the only man who can stop them.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: He tells you that you have to go to Mars.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: You'll need to get to Mars before the Russians do.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: You will use the Doomsday device to destroy the Russian base on Mars.
